=The Youth Memories=

2
00:01:30,120 --> 00:01:32,940
=Episode 31=

3
00:01:33,300 --> 00:01:35,420
(Closed in Three Days
Clearance Sale)

4
00:01:35,420 --> 00:01:37,660
(Day and Night Shop)

5
00:02:06,520 --> 00:02:08,560
I don't dare to get involved
in illegal operation.

6
00:02:13,080 --> 00:02:14,360
It's all your money.

7
00:02:14,520 --> 00:02:15,320
Take it back.

8
00:02:22,000 --> 00:02:22,880
Go, go.

9
00:02:35,640 --> 00:02:36,280
Hongjun,

10
00:02:36,640 --> 00:02:37,800
I just heard

11
00:02:38,200 --> 00:02:39,640
Qi Tian's shop was closed down.

12
00:02:40,760 --> 00:02:42,520
What can he do, then?

13
00:02:46,720 --> 00:02:47,960
He could have sold anything else.

14
00:02:49,480 --> 00:02:50,840
But he sold smuggled tobacco.

15
00:02:51,760 --> 00:02:53,480
Now in China, smuggled tobacco

16
00:02:53,480 --> 00:02:54,880
is officially illegal.

17
00:02:55,400 --> 00:02:57,080
His shop had to be closed down.

18
00:02:57,480 --> 00:02:59,600
When Chunsheng knows it
after he comes back from Yunnan,

19
00:02:59,800 --> 00:03:01,160
he'll be pissed off.

20
00:03:01,800 --> 00:03:03,320
Qi Tian never likes
to take the right path.

21
00:03:03,680 --> 00:03:05,440
It's just like a lesson for him.

22
00:03:07,760 --> 00:03:08,600
Listen, you guys.

23
00:03:09,440 --> 00:03:10,760
You have to behave yourselves.

24
00:03:11,520 --> 00:03:12,840
Don't go illegal ways.

25
00:03:13,200 --> 00:03:14,120
If you're in trouble,

26
00:03:14,280 --> 00:03:15,600
I won't get you out.

27
00:03:15,680 --> 00:03:17,080
What are you talking about, Hongjun?

28
00:03:17,720 --> 00:03:20,200
We do small businesses
and we won't have trouble.

29
00:03:20,200 --> 00:03:20,960
- Yeah.
- Right?

30
00:03:21,640 --> 00:03:22,440
Come on.

31
00:03:22,440 --> 00:03:23,600
- Come on.
- Cheers, Hongjun.

32
00:03:23,600 --> 00:03:24,040
Cheers.

33
00:03:28,440 --> 00:03:29,800
But I don't think Qi Tian

34
00:03:30,240 --> 00:03:31,800
will be defeated like this.

35
00:03:33,200 --> 00:03:34,720
Chunsheng is his brother-in-law.

36
00:03:34,920 --> 00:03:36,440
When he's back, he'll help more or less.

37
00:03:36,720 --> 00:03:37,840
He's faithful, after all.

38
00:03:44,120 --> 00:03:47,000
Chunsheng is not only faithful

39
00:03:47,200 --> 00:03:47,920
but also strong-willed.

40
00:03:49,120 --> 00:03:51,760
The most upstanding guys in the world.

41
00:03:54,680 --> 00:03:56,160
Hongjun, don't think about him.

42
00:03:56,360 --> 00:03:56,880
Let's drink.

43
00:03:57,080 --> 00:03:57,800
Yeah. Come on.

44
00:03:57,800 --> 00:03:58,400
Hongjun,

45
00:03:58,760 --> 00:03:59,840
let's drink together.

46
00:04:00,560 --> 00:04:00,960
Cheers.

47
00:04:03,480 --> 00:04:04,080
Bottoms up.

48
00:04:39,240 --> 00:04:41,280
Chunsheng just hasn't called for days

49
00:04:42,120 --> 00:04:43,200
and look at her.

50
00:04:43,640 --> 00:04:44,360
I think

51
00:04:44,640 --> 00:04:45,280
we should

52
00:04:46,720 --> 00:04:49,440
tie her to Chunsheng's belt.

53
00:04:49,880 --> 00:04:52,960
Wherever he goes, he can take you.

54
00:04:57,040 --> 00:04:58,480
She's a grown-up

55
00:04:58,840 --> 00:04:59,880
and we can't interfere.

56
00:05:04,240 --> 00:05:05,960
It's not what you think it is.

57
00:05:22,440 --> 00:05:23,040
What?

58
00:05:23,560 --> 00:05:24,480
Did you miss me?

59
00:05:25,000 --> 00:05:25,960
Chunsheng.

60
00:05:27,760 --> 00:05:29,240
My parents are home.

61
00:05:32,440 --> 00:05:32,800
I...

62
00:05:33,480 --> 00:05:35,680
I'm just back from Yunnan.

63
00:05:35,680 --> 00:05:36,760
And I brought some local food

64
00:05:36,760 --> 00:05:38,120
to Mr. and Mrs. Tong.

65
00:05:38,320 --> 00:05:41,040
I... I rushed over
after getting off the train.

66
00:05:41,040 --> 00:05:42,920
I didn't even go home.

67
00:05:43,720 --> 00:05:45,480
Why are you such a poseur?

68
00:05:46,440 --> 00:05:47,760
Who am I doing this for?

69
00:05:48,920 --> 00:05:49,680
Stop laughing.

70
00:05:50,120 --> 00:05:51,080
Get me in.

71
00:05:51,320 --> 00:05:53,040
Hurry. What are you waiting for?

72
00:05:53,040 --> 00:05:53,840
Come on in.

73
00:05:54,720 --> 00:05:55,560
Mr. and Mrs. Tong.

74
00:05:56,800 --> 00:05:57,800
There you are, Chunsheng.

75
00:05:58,080 --> 00:05:59,360
I'm just back from Yunnan

76
00:05:59,480 --> 00:06:00,920
and I brought you some local food.

77
00:06:01,680 --> 00:06:02,680
Look at him.

78
00:06:02,840 --> 00:06:03,960
He's good.

79
00:06:09,360 --> 00:06:10,080
Chunsheng,

80
00:06:12,240 --> 00:06:14,560
do you have any plans?

81
00:06:18,080 --> 00:06:18,520
Dad.

82
00:06:22,520 --> 00:06:23,240
See?

83
00:06:24,200 --> 00:06:25,000
Xiaomei

84
00:06:25,280 --> 00:06:26,960
defends Chunsheng all the time

85
00:06:27,440 --> 00:06:29,000
in case I talk harshly.

86
00:06:29,240 --> 00:06:30,200
Yes, she does.

87
00:06:30,920 --> 00:06:31,360
Let's eat.

88
00:06:32,200 --> 00:06:32,760
Mr. Tong.

89
00:06:33,360 --> 00:06:34,200
You're right.

90
00:06:34,920 --> 00:06:36,880
Xiaomei cares really a lot about me.

91
00:06:38,920 --> 00:06:39,800
Thank you, Mrs. Tong.

92
00:06:42,000 --> 00:06:44,840
Mr. Tong, I still decide
to start a business.

93
00:06:46,120 --> 00:06:47,400
I used to think

94
00:06:47,440 --> 00:06:48,880
joining the army was the only way

95
00:06:48,920 --> 00:06:50,160
to serve the people.

96
00:06:50,920 --> 00:06:52,600
But times have changed.

97
00:06:52,840 --> 00:06:54,240
I had a trip to the South

98
00:06:54,480 --> 00:06:56,400
and I've broadened my horizon.

99
00:06:57,160 --> 00:06:58,400
The government also says

100
00:06:58,520 --> 00:07:01,240
more power is needed
to develop the national economy.

101
00:07:01,640 --> 00:07:04,320
Starting a business will be supported.

102
00:07:08,360 --> 00:07:10,760
Sounds like you've made up your mind.

103
00:07:13,040 --> 00:07:13,960
In this case,

104
00:07:14,720 --> 00:07:17,320
so much for the Anti-smuggling Squad.

105
00:07:17,680 --> 00:07:18,360
Let's not bring it up again.

106
00:07:20,040 --> 00:07:21,240
We're getting old

107
00:07:21,480 --> 00:07:22,800
and we can offer little help.

108
00:07:23,240 --> 00:07:24,040
But

109
00:07:25,000 --> 00:07:26,760
we sincerely hope

110
00:07:26,920 --> 00:07:30,480
whatever industry you work in,

111
00:07:31,680 --> 00:07:33,200
you'll try to be the best.

112
00:07:37,160 --> 00:07:38,800
Mr. and Mrs. Tong,

113
00:07:39,160 --> 00:07:39,840
don't worry.

114
00:07:40,560 --> 00:07:42,320
Now, I have no money.

115
00:07:42,600 --> 00:07:43,800
But I'm aggressive.

116
00:07:44,280 --> 00:07:46,160
I'll work hard to achieve something

117
00:07:46,480 --> 00:07:48,480
and make myself good enough for Xiaomei.

118
00:07:53,040 --> 00:07:53,800
Come on.

119
00:07:55,360 --> 00:07:56,720
Drink with me.

120
00:07:56,840 --> 00:07:57,960
Mr. Tong, a toast to you.

121
00:07:59,800 --> 00:08:00,200
Cheers.

122
00:08:00,360 --> 00:08:00,800
Cheers.

123
00:08:00,920 --> 00:08:01,440
Come on, Xiaomei.

124
00:08:01,840 --> 00:08:02,280
Cheers, Mrs. Tong.

125
00:08:04,360 --> 00:08:05,080
Come on.

126
00:08:18,320 --> 00:08:19,000
Wake up.

127
00:08:20,880 --> 00:08:22,080
Time for breakfast.

128
00:08:24,080 --> 00:08:25,200
I'm going to work.

129
00:08:40,360 --> 00:08:41,030
Yanqiu.

130
00:08:43,000 --> 00:08:43,720
You're back?

131
00:08:44,320 --> 00:08:45,120
Yes, for a couple of days.

132
00:08:46,920 --> 00:08:49,240
Yanqiu, Xiaomei told me

133
00:08:49,840 --> 00:08:50,920
about your shop.

134
00:08:57,240 --> 00:08:57,800
Yanqiu,

135
00:08:58,440 --> 00:08:59,360
what's this?

136
00:09:00,680 --> 00:09:02,720
My neighbor got a job
of paper-box making.

137
00:09:02,880 --> 00:09:03,960
I'm doing this for some little money.

138
00:09:05,440 --> 00:09:06,120
What about Qi Tian?

139
00:09:07,600 --> 00:09:08,480
Sleeping.

140
00:09:12,680 --> 00:09:13,880
Don't bully him!

141
00:09:19,520 --> 00:09:20,640
Leave it to me.

142
00:09:23,360 --> 00:09:24,040
Get up.

143
00:09:27,480 --> 00:09:29,000
I said, get up! Do you hear?

144
00:09:37,520 --> 00:09:38,960
Is this how you take care of my sister?

145
00:09:42,880 --> 00:09:43,760
I've just been...

146
00:09:43,760 --> 00:09:44,440
So, it's the reason

147
00:09:44,440 --> 00:09:46,280
you sleep till noon?

148
00:09:47,520 --> 00:09:48,480
It's the reason you make your wife

149
00:09:48,480 --> 00:09:50,000
do paper-box making?

150
00:09:51,680 --> 00:09:52,760
Qi Tian, listen.

151
00:09:53,720 --> 00:09:55,320
My sister isn't a finicky woman.

152
00:09:55,560 --> 00:09:56,800
But she's now your wife.

153
00:09:57,760 --> 00:09:59,760
If you make her suffer and bully her,

154
00:10:00,920 --> 00:10:02,840
I won't even care about our friendship.

155
00:10:08,880 --> 00:10:09,600
Chief Xiong.

156
00:10:09,960 --> 00:10:11,720
You're Jiefang's comrade-in-arms.

157
00:10:12,080 --> 00:10:13,200
Then you're my comrade-in-arms.

158
00:10:13,640 --> 00:10:15,840
Soldiers like us are a family.

159
00:10:17,280 --> 00:10:18,280
And don't get me wrong.

160
00:10:18,520 --> 00:10:19,800
I invite you to dinner

161
00:10:19,960 --> 00:10:22,320
just to make friendly contacts.

162
00:10:22,600 --> 00:10:23,600
I don't mean anything else.

163
00:10:24,200 --> 00:10:25,200
(Draft beer)
What are you talking about?

164
00:10:25,840 --> 00:10:26,680
You know what, Chunsheng?

165
00:10:27,200 --> 00:10:29,200
You're from a compound. So am I.

166
00:10:29,520 --> 00:10:30,720
You're from a military compound

167
00:10:30,960 --> 00:10:32,200
and I'm from a foreign trade compound.

168
00:10:32,880 --> 00:10:33,440
And you know what?

169
00:10:33,920 --> 00:10:35,440
Xiao Chunsheng's name

170
00:10:35,440 --> 00:10:38,040
has got very popular among my buddies

171
00:10:38,120 --> 00:10:39,560
in my compound.

172
00:10:39,840 --> 00:10:41,720
Today, I can drink beer with Chunsheng.

173
00:10:41,920 --> 00:10:42,960
And I'm really happy.

174
00:10:43,160 --> 00:10:43,800
Come on.

175
00:10:43,960 --> 00:10:45,720
Let's drink together, OK?

176
00:10:45,720 --> 00:10:46,560
Come on.

177
00:10:46,560 --> 00:10:47,280
Cheers.

178
00:10:53,080 --> 00:10:53,840
Feels great.

179
00:10:54,600 --> 00:10:55,520
Xiong, let me tell you this.

180
00:10:55,720 --> 00:10:57,240
Chunsheng is my best buddy.

181
00:10:57,880 --> 00:11:00,080
He invited you to dinner here

182
00:11:00,200 --> 00:11:02,720
and it means he's taking you
as a friend, got it?

183
00:11:03,080 --> 00:11:04,840
Comrades-in-arms and good friends.

184
00:11:05,440 --> 00:11:06,840
Chunsheng, listen.

185
00:11:06,960 --> 00:11:08,840
If you need help, tell him.

186
00:11:08,920 --> 00:11:09,840
Don't hesitate.

187
00:11:11,040 --> 00:11:12,120
Jiefang is right.

188
00:11:12,440 --> 00:11:14,640
If you need anything, let me know.

189
00:11:14,840 --> 00:11:17,000
Friends like us don't need
to be punctilious, OK?

190
00:11:17,800 --> 00:11:20,040
Fine. I'll get to the point, then.

191
00:11:20,560 --> 00:11:22,320
My friend in Kunming and I

192
00:11:22,440 --> 00:11:24,680
want to do business in jade jewelry.

193
00:11:25,320 --> 00:11:26,440
My friend is Xiang Nan.

194
00:11:26,720 --> 00:11:28,280
He has his stores in Kunming

195
00:11:28,640 --> 00:11:30,440
and a hand-me-down traditional workshop.

196
00:11:31,040 --> 00:11:31,960
Now, we have

197
00:11:32,040 --> 00:11:33,960
a large stash of jade jewelry.

198
00:11:34,440 --> 00:11:35,200
I wonder

199
00:11:35,600 --> 00:11:36,680
if we can do this business

200
00:11:36,960 --> 00:11:38,080
here in Beijing.

201
00:11:39,720 --> 00:11:40,400
I get you.

202
00:11:41,440 --> 00:11:43,720
So, you want to cooperate

203
00:11:43,720 --> 00:11:44,560
with us, BACC Service.
[*Beijing Arts and Crafts Corporation]

204
00:11:45,040 --> 00:11:45,920
Am I right?

205
00:11:46,440 --> 00:11:47,840
Yes, that's what I mean.

206
00:11:48,200 --> 00:11:49,080
I'd like to know

207
00:11:49,640 --> 00:11:50,840
if we can cooperate.

208
00:11:51,720 --> 00:11:52,680
Yes.

209
00:11:53,280 --> 00:11:54,440
Of course.

210
00:11:55,400 --> 00:11:56,280
Let me tell you this, Chunsheng.

211
00:11:56,440 --> 00:11:57,920
BACC is

212
00:11:58,080 --> 00:12:00,200
China's biggest company

213
00:12:00,360 --> 00:12:02,720
in arts and crafts.

214
00:12:03,520 --> 00:12:05,040
Jade jewelry also belongs

215
00:12:05,120 --> 00:12:06,720
to arts and crafts.

216
00:12:07,720 --> 00:12:08,440
And you know what?

217
00:12:08,800 --> 00:12:11,400
The biggest jade processing plant in Beijing

218
00:12:11,600 --> 00:12:13,640
is also affiliated to BACC.

219
00:12:14,120 --> 00:12:16,440
Every year, we produce vast amounts

220
00:12:16,440 --> 00:12:18,200
of jade jewelry and jade ornaments.

221
00:12:18,720 --> 00:12:21,200
Some of them are sold overseas

222
00:12:21,440 --> 00:12:22,920
to get export earnings for our country.

223
00:12:23,640 --> 00:12:24,440
The rest of them

224
00:12:24,560 --> 00:12:26,960
are sold in local BACC Services.

225
00:12:28,440 --> 00:12:29,680
You're saying

226
00:12:30,080 --> 00:12:31,680
you produce what you sell.

227
00:12:32,640 --> 00:12:35,040
Then what about our jade jewelry?

228
00:12:36,040 --> 00:12:37,200
Hear me out.

229
00:12:38,520 --> 00:12:39,600
BACC Service

230
00:12:40,120 --> 00:12:42,960
has points of sale

231
00:12:43,640 --> 00:12:44,400
in some big foreign-related hotels.

232
00:12:44,840 --> 00:12:47,000
A large supply is needed, then.

233
00:12:48,040 --> 00:12:49,840
We not only produce our own jewels,

234
00:12:50,200 --> 00:12:52,960
but also cooperate with many jewelers

235
00:12:53,120 --> 00:12:54,280
on a commission basis.

236
00:12:54,920 --> 00:12:55,800
Do you understand?

237
00:12:56,920 --> 00:12:57,360
Yes.

238
00:12:58,200 --> 00:13:00,280
How do you cooperate then?

239
00:13:01,280 --> 00:13:02,160
We do this.

240
00:13:03,160 --> 00:13:06,160
You give us your jewels

241
00:13:06,840 --> 00:13:08,120
and we fix a price.

242
00:13:08,600 --> 00:13:09,160
Then,

243
00:13:09,480 --> 00:13:10,440
based on this price,

244
00:13:10,680 --> 00:13:11,840
BACC Service

245
00:13:12,160 --> 00:13:13,600
will give a floating price.

246
00:13:14,080 --> 00:13:16,200
After the jewels are sold,

247
00:13:16,840 --> 00:13:18,520
we'll give you the money

248
00:13:18,640 --> 00:13:19,360
according to the fixed price.

249
00:13:19,760 --> 00:13:20,280
In this way,

250
00:13:20,600 --> 00:13:21,440
you get profit.

251
00:13:21,760 --> 00:13:22,880
So do we.

252
00:13:23,120 --> 00:13:23,800
Got it?

253
00:13:24,120 --> 00:13:24,720
Yes.

254
00:13:25,320 --> 00:13:27,480
How is the price fixed then?

255
00:13:28,560 --> 00:13:29,200
Oh, this.

256
00:13:30,000 --> 00:13:31,160
We have

257
00:13:31,400 --> 00:13:32,480
hired some old experts

258
00:13:32,640 --> 00:13:35,160
in jade jewelry

259
00:13:35,800 --> 00:13:37,800
and craftsmen of jade carving.

260
00:13:38,040 --> 00:13:40,360
They check the jewels and price them.

261
00:13:41,880 --> 00:13:44,520
There's a Master Jin

262
00:13:45,800 --> 00:13:47,320
whose ancestors

263
00:13:47,320 --> 00:13:49,520
made jewels for the emperor

264
00:13:49,600 --> 00:13:52,040
and Empress Dowager Cixi.

265
00:13:53,520 --> 00:13:54,240
You know what?

266
00:13:54,400 --> 00:13:56,720
Master Jin is in his sixties

267
00:13:57,320 --> 00:13:58,280
and he retired.

268
00:13:58,760 --> 00:13:59,520
But we especially

269
00:13:59,520 --> 00:14:01,760
reemployed him.

270
00:14:01,960 --> 00:14:03,880
He checks the jewels, prices them,

271
00:14:04,520 --> 00:14:05,520
and meanwhile,

272
00:14:05,880 --> 00:14:06,920
he teaches young craftsmen

273
00:14:07,040 --> 00:14:09,400
to do some jade carving.

274
00:14:10,560 --> 00:14:12,120
Master Jin is

275
00:14:12,200 --> 00:14:14,320
a national treasure.

276
00:14:14,440 --> 00:14:15,680
The real master.

277
00:14:16,480 --> 00:14:18,120
There's a saying in BACC Service

278
00:14:18,560 --> 00:14:21,240
that an old master counts on nothing,

279
00:14:21,600 --> 00:14:23,520
but his experience and skills.

280
00:14:24,440 --> 00:14:25,240
Don't worry, Chunsheng.

281
00:14:25,480 --> 00:14:27,520
For all jewels you supply,

282
00:14:27,840 --> 00:14:30,360
I'll have Master Jin
check them personally.

283
00:14:30,760 --> 00:14:32,360
And the price will be good.

284
00:14:32,560 --> 00:14:34,040
I won't make you lose money,

285
00:14:34,040 --> 00:14:34,640
right?

286
00:14:35,360 --> 00:14:36,280
Then I get nothing else to ask.

287
00:14:36,440 --> 00:14:37,520
Let's do the business, OK?

288
00:14:38,600 --> 00:14:39,640
