00:26:56,440 --> 00:26:57,400
That pendant,

580
00:26:57,400 --> 00:26:58,840
it can sell at any price.

581
00:26:59,360 --> 00:27:01,440
Nan, don't only care about money.

582
00:27:01,840 --> 00:27:03,000
That's a work of art.

583
00:27:03,160 --> 00:27:04,240
And art is priceless.

584
00:27:04,880 --> 00:27:05,680
Yes, yes.

585
00:27:06,680 --> 00:27:08,040
You make me

586
00:27:08,040 --> 00:27:09,360
so eager to look at it.

587
00:27:09,640 --> 00:27:11,240
I wonder if I have the luck.

588
00:27:11,600 --> 00:27:13,480
We've got to know Master Jin

589
00:27:13,760 --> 00:27:14,760
and there'll be chances.

590
00:27:15,200 --> 00:27:15,840
That's right.

591
00:27:16,040 --> 00:27:17,600
Go with us next time, OK?

592
00:27:17,600 --> 00:27:19,120
- OK. Let's go together.
- Come on.

593
00:27:19,360 --> 00:27:20,440
Cheers.

594
00:27:20,440 --> 00:27:21,120
Cheers.

595
00:27:21,600 --> 00:27:22,200
Come on.

596
00:27:26,560 --> 00:27:27,120
By the way,

597
00:27:27,480 --> 00:27:28,400
Chunsheng, Xiaomei,

598
00:27:28,960 --> 00:27:31,400
I'm going back to Yunnan tomorrow.

599
00:27:34,000 --> 00:27:36,200
Nan, why not stay a few more days?

600
00:27:36,400 --> 00:27:37,480
BACC bought

601
00:27:37,640 --> 00:27:38,600
all the jade jewels I brought here.

602
00:27:39,120 --> 00:27:40,680
I have nothing to do, then.

603
00:27:41,080 --> 00:27:41,760
My plan is

604
00:27:41,960 --> 00:27:42,960
I go back to Yunnan

605
00:27:43,160 --> 00:27:45,320
and buy some raw jade
from Tengchong and Ruili.

606
00:27:45,760 --> 00:27:48,280
Then I'll have some products
made for BACC.

607
00:27:48,760 --> 00:27:49,640
You made sense.

608
00:27:50,080 --> 00:27:52,040
If BACC Service sells

609
00:27:52,400 --> 00:27:53,640
the products we supplied,

610
00:27:53,640 --> 00:27:54,680
they'll soon be sold out.

611
00:27:55,600 --> 00:27:56,960
Fine, Nan.

612
00:27:57,160 --> 00:27:58,920
I'll count on you for the supply.

613
00:27:59,280 --> 00:28:00,800
Count on me.

614
00:28:03,520 --> 00:28:04,680
But... Umm...

615
00:28:05,840 --> 00:28:06,640
I wonder

616
00:28:07,360 --> 00:28:09,160
if I should say something.

617
00:28:09,760 --> 00:28:11,000
Come on, we're friends.

618
00:28:11,120 --> 00:28:11,800
Just tell me.

619
00:28:13,680 --> 00:28:14,640
To be honest,

620
00:28:15,680 --> 00:28:17,160
I spent most of my money

621
00:28:17,280 --> 00:28:18,720
on the goods

622
00:28:18,720 --> 00:28:20,920
sold in my stores in Kunming

623
00:28:21,040 --> 00:28:23,240
and the products for BACC.

624
00:28:23,760 --> 00:28:25,240
I'll have to give a large supply

625
00:28:25,240 --> 00:28:26,520
to BACC again.

626
00:28:27,280 --> 00:28:30,680
I'm... I'm a little bit short of money.

627
00:28:32,400 --> 00:28:33,160
Yeah.

628
00:28:34,120 --> 00:28:35,320
It's quite a large supply.

629
00:28:36,120 --> 00:28:37,560
How much money do you need?

630
00:28:38,160 --> 00:28:40,560
Nan, you should have told me earlier.

631
00:28:40,960 --> 00:28:42,520
How much more do you need?
I'll take care of it.

632
00:28:44,480 --> 00:28:45,120
Fine.

633
00:28:45,680 --> 00:28:48,120
Chunsheng, now that we cooperate,

634
00:28:48,400 --> 00:28:49,600
I won't play hard to get.

635
00:28:50,600 --> 00:28:52,480
Give me as much money as you can.

636
00:28:52,560 --> 00:28:53,920
And I'll take care of the rest.

637
00:28:56,000 --> 00:28:57,440
OK. Let's do this.

638
00:28:57,800 --> 00:28:58,760
You return to Kunming tomorrow.

639
00:28:59,280 --> 00:29:00,880
I'll get as much money as I can

640
00:29:01,120 --> 00:29:02,480
and then transfer it to you.

641
00:29:02,720 --> 00:29:04,240
OK. It's a deal, then.

642
00:29:04,320 --> 00:29:04,680
OK.

643
00:29:04,680 --> 00:29:05,160
Come on.

644
00:29:05,400 --> 00:29:05,760
Cheers.

645
00:29:06,520 --> 00:29:07,600
You have to drink it up.

646
00:29:15,280 --> 00:29:17,200
Nan is really fun.

647
00:29:21,760 --> 00:29:25,160
Chunsheng, you promised
to get some money for him.

648
00:29:25,680 --> 00:29:27,000
Have you thought about how to get it?

649
00:29:30,280 --> 00:29:32,000
Nan was telling the truth.

650
00:29:32,200 --> 00:29:34,480
We can't get money
from BACC very quickly.

651
00:29:35,040 --> 00:29:35,680
Think about it.

652
00:29:36,000 --> 00:29:37,800
If I didn't help him, who else would?

653
00:29:39,480 --> 00:29:41,120
Then how will you help him?

654
00:29:43,920 --> 00:29:46,320
I have some demobilization compensation

655
00:29:46,920 --> 00:29:49,080
and some savings from my previous job.

656
00:29:49,680 --> 00:29:50,520
Not a lot.

657
00:29:51,040 --> 00:29:52,160
But it's better than nothing.

658
00:29:54,440 --> 00:29:55,680
I have some savings.

659
00:29:56,120 --> 00:29:57,400
I'll give them to you tomorrow.

660
00:29:58,480 --> 00:30:01,200
Xiaomei, how could I take your money?

661
00:30:01,600 --> 00:30:03,240
But we're a couple.

662
00:30:04,520 --> 00:30:05,600
Don't bother about this.

663
00:30:06,000 --> 00:30:06,400
Well,

664
00:30:06,680 --> 00:30:08,360
tomorrow, I'll visit my sister and Tian

665
00:30:08,440 --> 00:30:09,440
and ask them to think of a way.

666
00:30:11,040 --> 00:30:11,840
OK.

667
00:30:12,440 --> 00:30:13,160
You call the shots.

668
00:30:15,200 --> 00:30:16,160
But Chunsheng,

669
00:30:16,600 --> 00:30:17,880
you have only a little money.

670
00:30:18,160 --> 00:30:19,880
Even if you get some from others,

671
00:30:20,200 --> 00:30:21,560
you can't afford a piece of raw material.

672
00:30:23,040 --> 00:30:25,800
Nan must be aware of that.

673
00:30:26,200 --> 00:30:27,800
But he asked you for money.

674
00:30:28,920 --> 00:30:30,480
Isn't it weird?

675
00:30:32,600 --> 00:30:33,960
I know him very well.

676
00:30:34,520 --> 00:30:35,560
It's not weird.

677
00:30:36,400 --> 00:30:37,720
He asked me for it

678
00:30:38,480 --> 00:30:39,520
and I promised him.

679
00:30:40,440 --> 00:30:41,680
Then I have to do my best.

680
00:30:42,560 --> 00:30:43,200
Don't worry.

681
00:30:58,680 --> 00:31:00,360
You're playing with jade jewelry?

682
00:31:00,880 --> 00:31:02,040
What are you talking about?

683
00:31:02,760 --> 00:31:03,760
Tian, do you remember?

684
00:31:04,480 --> 00:31:05,600
Back in Kunming,

685
00:31:05,600 --> 00:31:07,360
I once saved a jade jeweler,

686
00:31:07,360 --> 00:31:08,080
Xiang Nan.

687
00:31:08,280 --> 00:31:09,720
Yes, I remember.

688
00:31:10,600 --> 00:31:13,120
When I went to Kunming, he came to me,

689
00:31:13,520 --> 00:31:16,120
asking me to get his business to Beijing.

690
00:31:16,680 --> 00:31:17,720
I then asked a friend of mine

691
00:31:17,720 --> 00:31:18,680
to contact someone

692
00:31:18,680 --> 00:31:20,040
from BACC.

693
00:31:20,360 --> 00:31:22,440
The first batch of products
are being sold already.

694
00:31:23,480 --> 00:31:24,720
Well done, Chunsheng.

695
00:31:26,040 --> 00:31:28,000
Jade jewelry is a great business.

696
00:31:28,680 --> 00:31:30,120
You must have earned a lot.

697
00:31:31,640 --> 00:31:32,920
I was just helping him

698
00:31:32,920 --> 00:31:34,000
and it's not my business.

699
00:31:34,120 --> 00:31:35,360
Why is it not?

700
00:31:35,360 --> 00:31:36,000
Without you,

701
00:31:36,000 --> 00:31:37,920
he couldn't have sold
his jewels in Beijing.

702
00:31:38,440 --> 00:31:39,160
All right, Tian.

703
00:31:39,440 --> 00:31:40,400
Let's drop this topic.

704
00:31:41,000 --> 00:31:42,000
Today, I came to you

705
00:31:42,240 --> 00:31:44,880
just because Xiang Nan invested too much

706
00:31:45,440 --> 00:31:46,480
and he's short of money now.

707
00:31:47,120 --> 00:31:47,880
I want to help him.

708
00:31:48,960 --> 00:31:49,600
Go ahead.

709
00:31:49,960 --> 00:31:51,200
We should help him.

710
00:31:51,400 --> 00:31:52,720
Tell me, Chunsheng. How much?

711
00:31:53,040 --> 00:31:53,720
Any amount.

712
00:31:54,240 --> 00:31:55,400
You're quite boasting.

713
00:31:55,880 --> 00:31:56,640
Do you have money?

714
00:31:56,960 --> 00:31:58,840
Then why does my sister
do paper-box making?

715
00:32:00,880 --> 00:32:02,160
Tian, I didn't come

716
00:32:02,360 --> 00:32:03,400
to borrow money.

717
00:32:03,920 --> 00:32:06,280
I just think you have many friends
and you're respected.

718
00:32:07,560 --> 00:32:09,920
Could you help me

719
00:32:10,160 --> 00:32:12,760
to borrow some money
from your rich friends?

720
00:32:14,080 --> 00:32:14,800
Don't worry.

721
00:32:15,000 --> 00:32:16,800
When we get the money from BACC,

722
00:32:16,960 --> 00:32:17,800
I'll return the money immediately.

723
00:32:18,160 --> 00:32:19,560
Who do you want to borrow from?

724
00:32:19,560 --> 00:32:20,280
Who?

725
00:32:20,280 --> 00:32:21,400
When you need money,

726
00:32:21,760 --> 00:32:23,840
just tell your sister and me.

727
00:32:24,240 --> 00:32:25,040
You?

728
00:32:26,720 --> 00:32:29,200
Chunsheng, don't underestimate us.

729
00:32:29,600 --> 00:32:30,320
You know what?

730
00:32:30,600 --> 00:32:32,760
I lost my shop, but I'm not broke.

731
00:32:33,160 --> 00:32:34,840
I've been doing business
for so many years.

732
00:32:35,560 --> 00:32:37,160
And I have some savings.

733
00:32:38,160 --> 00:32:39,480
Don't boast, Tian.

734
00:32:39,920 --> 00:32:40,640
You have savings?

735
00:32:40,640 --> 00:32:42,480
Then why does my sister
do paper-box making?

736
00:32:44,960 --> 00:32:46,640
You have to ask her.

737
00:32:46,960 --> 00:32:49,280
I quarreled with her
over this several times.

738
00:32:49,600 --> 00:32:51,520
I said we had savings

739
00:32:51,600 --> 00:32:53,680
and she didn't need to do that work.

740
00:32:53,840 --> 00:32:54,680
Do you know what she said?

741
00:32:55,160 --> 00:32:57,080
"Using the savings
will be depleting our resources

742
00:32:57,200 --> 00:32:58,320
and then the money will be gone."

743
00:32:58,520 --> 00:33:00,800
She doesn't allow me to use the savings.

744
00:33:01,400 --> 00:33:02,400
Well, she's right.

745
00:33:02,680 --> 00:33:04,400
We need money for emergencies.

746
00:33:04,720 --> 00:33:05,320
Right?

747
00:33:07,760 --> 00:33:08,480
You know what?

748
00:33:09,160 --> 00:33:11,280
It's the way my sister is.

749
00:33:11,960 --> 00:33:12,840
She's hard-working.

750
00:33:13,480 --> 00:33:15,280
Right. She loves to work hard.

751
00:33:16,040 --> 00:33:18,200
But luckily, she keeps the money.

752
00:33:18,320 --> 00:33:20,480
Otherwise, I would have used it up.

753
00:33:22,600 --> 00:33:23,160
See?

754
00:33:24,640 --> 00:33:26,160
Now, it's needed.

755
00:33:26,480 --> 00:33:27,760
Well, Tian,

756
00:33:28,520 --> 00:33:30,040
discuss it with my sister tonight.

757
00:33:30,520 --> 00:33:31,720
If she approves,

758
00:33:32,240 --> 00:33:33,280
give the money to me.

759
00:33:34,040 --> 00:33:34,800
Don't worry.

760
00:33:34,960 --> 00:33:36,200
I know Xiang Nan very well.

761
00:33:36,520 --> 00:33:38,120
He won't borrow the money for nothing.

762
00:33:38,720 --> 00:33:39,840
Just tell my sister this.

763
00:33:40,040 --> 00:33:41,360
Tell her lending the money to us

764
00:33:41,600 --> 00:33:43,400
will get a higher interest rate
than saving it in the bank.

765
00:33:44,480 --> 00:33:45,840
What are you talking about?

766
00:33:46,440 --> 00:33:47,200
Chunsheng,

767
00:33:48,720 --> 00:33:51,080
since my shop was closed down,

768
00:33:51,080 --> 00:33:52,040
I've been thinking

769
00:33:52,160 --> 00:33:53,720
what else I can do.

770
00:33:53,800 --> 00:33:56,800
See? It's a golden chance for me.

771
00:33:57,440 --> 00:33:59,640
Jade jewelry. What a great business!

772
00:33:59,920 --> 00:34:01,120
Mr. Xiang is experienced.

773
00:34:01,120 --> 00:34:02,320
And you have the distribution channel.

774
00:34:02,680 --> 00:34:04,360
We can make money
as easily as we can imagine.

775
00:34:07,400 --> 00:34:07,800
Chunsheng,

776
00:34:07,800 --> 00:34:10,840
how about you discuss it with Mr. Xiang?

777
00:34:11,150 --> 00:34:12,480
Take my money for shareholding

778
00:34:12,760 --> 00:34:13,560
and we can do business together.

779
00:34:13,560 --> 00:34:14,320
What do you say?

780
00:34:14,840 --> 00:34:17,520
Tian, nice try.

781
00:34:17,960 --> 00:34:18,800
Share?

782
00:34:21,280 --> 00:34:22,230
Let me tell you something.

783
00:34:22,670 --> 00:34:24,320
Xiang Nan indeed asked me

784
00:34:24,320 --> 00:34:25,190
to be his business partner.

785
00:34:25,520 --> 00:34:26,560
But I didn't accept it.

786
00:34:27,120 --> 00:34:29,520
For BACC, I just did him a favor.

787
00:34:30,230 --> 00:34:31,190
And,

788
00:34:31,520 --> 00:34:33,560
we only have this little money.

789
00:34:34,190 --> 00:34:35,080
I'm too ashamed to ask for shareholding.

790
00:34:36,630 --> 00:34:38,920
Chunsheng, this is your problem.

791
00:34:39,280 --> 00:34:40,800
You stand too much in pride.

792
00:34:42,120 --> 00:34:44,000
I know you don't want
to take advantage of him.

793
00:34:44,670 --> 00:34:45,710
I won't push you.

794
00:34:46,230 --> 00:34:47,710
Tonight, I'll discuss it with your sister.

795
00:34:47,880 --> 00:34:48,630
If she approves,

796
00:34:48,630 --> 00:34:49,800
I'll give you the money tomorrow.

797
00:34:50,760 --> 00:34:52,800
And whether I lend it to you

798
00:34:52,800 --> 00:34:54,710
or I give it for shareholding,

799
00:34:55,440 --> 00:34:56,400
I'll listen to you.

800
00:34:56,880 --> 00:34:57,480
You call the shots.

801
00:34:58,920 --> 00:34:59,520
OK.

802
00:35:04,080 --> 00:35:05,400
I received the money transfer.

803
00:35:06,140 --> 00:35:06,780
(Remittance Notice of China Post)

804
00:35:06,780 --> 00:35:09,760
You've really offered timely help.

805
00:35:10,840 --> 00:35:13,320
Nan, don't tease me.

806
00:35:13,640 --> 00:35:14,680
This little money I give you

807
00:35:14,840 --> 00:35:16,320
can't help you a lot.

808
00:35:16,600 --> 00:35:18,120
The amount doesn't matter.

809
00:35:18,240 --> 00:35:20,480
Our friendship matters.

810
00:35:22,760 --> 00:35:24,760
Nan, I'm calling you

811
00:35:24,960 --> 00:35:25,800
to tell you something.

812
00:35:26,120 --> 00:35:27,800
Chief Xiong from BACC told me

813
00:35:27,920 --> 00:35:29,480
your products sold very well

814
00:35:29,760 --> 00:35:31,600
and he asked you to deliver some more.

815
00:35:31,800 --> 00:35:32,960
The products are ready.

816
00:35:33,160 --> 00:35:34,120
I'm going to Beijing tomorrow.

817
00:35:36,640 --> 00:35:39,560
But Nan, I just transferred the money
a couple of days ago.

818
00:35:39,680 --> 00:35:40,920
And the products are ready?

819
00:35:42,920 --> 00:35:44,560
Don't bother about it.

820
00:35:44,800 --> 00:35:45,760
Wait for me in Beijing.

821
00:35:46,560 --> 00:35:47,960
OK. I'll be waiting.

822
00:36:01,880 --> 00:36:03,280
This one is the best.

823
00:36:04,880 --> 00:36:05,720
30,000 yuan.

824
00:36:09,120 --> 00:36:09,840
What did I say?

825
00:36:09,840 --> 00:36:11,040
Master Jin will give you a high price.

826
00:36:13,600 --> 00:36:14,400
5,000 yuan.

827
00:36:14,800 --> 00:36:16,560
This one is indeed poorly carved.

828
00:36:16,560 --> 00:36:17,440
But the material is good.

829
00:36:17,440 --> 00:36:17,920
Right.

830
00:36:17,920 --> 00:36:18,560
It's good.

831
00:36:21,400 --> 00:36:22,880
This one looks better.

832
00:36:22,880 --> 00:36:23,800
25,000 yuan.

833
00:36:30,680 --> 00:36:32,920
This one... Better than that one.

834
00:36:32,960 --> 00:36:34,640
Here. Check this.

835
00:36:35,240 --> 00:36:36,200
Money for the products.

836
00:36:36,200 --> 00:36:37,260
(Commercial Acceptance Bill)

837
00:36:40,280 --> 00:36:41,240
Thank you, thank you.

838
00:36:41,680 --> 00:36:42,640
You're welcome.

839
00:36:42,640 --> 00:36:43,640
Thank you so much.

840
00:36:43,640 --> 00:36:44,600
Not at all.

841
00:36:47,080 --> 00:36:48,400
Come on, let's drink.

842
00:36:48,480 --> 00:36:49,560
Cheers.

843
00:36:50,080 --> 00:36:50,720
Come on.

844
00:36:50,720 --> 00:36:51,280
Cheers, Tian.

845
00:36:56,720 --> 00:36:58,600
Qi Tian isn't an outsider.

846
00:36:59,560 --> 00:37:00,920
We're a family, then.

847
00:37:02,000 --> 00:37:03,240
In my toughest time,

848
00:37:03,480 --> 00:37:04,440
you helped me.

849
00:37:05,200 --> 00:37:07,880
I wouldn't say thank you.

850
00:37:14,320 --> 00:37:16,120
Nan, returning the money so soon?

851
00:37:16,440 --> 00:37:18,000
Not returning the money,

852
00:37:18,680 --> 00:37:19,640
but giving you the dividends.

853
00:37:22,240 --> 00:37:23,640
This is too much.

854
00:37:26,080 --> 00:37:26,560
But...

855
00:37:33,200 --> 00:37:35,040
Nan, what do you mean?

856
00:37:35,800 --> 00:37:37,360
It's half of the profit

857
00:37:37,360 --> 00:37:39,240
from our first batch
of products to BACC.

858
00:37:39,760 --> 00:37:42,120
You deserve the money.

859
00:37:43,480 --> 00:37:45,320
I can't accept this. Take it back.

860
00:37:48,040 --> 00:37:49,360
I knew you wouldn't accept it.

